{"tid":2086114,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[大台重臨]原來香港眾志同黃色經濟圈係大台","createTime":"2020-06-30T07:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T13:38:54.000Z","uid":6752,"like":1151,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":130,"replies":[{"pid":"adefd78ed9b639bedcb9ec62a0d70f35e71e8815","tid":2086114,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"當初支共瘋狂老屈係大台既泛民,民陣,眾志之類既組織<br />\n以為斬左ed領袖大家就會散水<br />\n<br />\n但自從大家識玩冇大台,冇左e d形式上既領袖<br />\n成個運動就變左新模式<br />\n國安法過左,自稱黃圈,甚至點名既反對派一定會比人搞<br />\n家下檯面上唔可以再光明正大標籤自己<br />\n<br />\n係時候諗番咩叫去大台,還原1年前大家做過既野<br />\n人人都係領袖,自己諗應該去做乜啦<br />\n<br />\n龍門退出黃圈? 眾志解散?<br />\nWFC"},{"pid":"70393365bfed4aef2e7c0b26fd6a7ce6c52f9b04","tid":2086114,"uid":235316,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook ig airdrop</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=eae3d5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qizj3Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQizj3Rf.jpg&h=d33e105b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg0OXbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0OXbk.jpg&h=791a8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivfSEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivfSEpG.jpg&h=e07fd1e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17fa81f41e373f353411c9ae5345c57fc575d7ab","tid":2086114,"uid":151074,"like":164,"dislike":6,"score":158,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"原來黃圈係一個組織係可以退岀，我宜家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/